channel.title: [RS2][SRL]Bobert5696's Fight Cave Machine NOW RELEASED FOR FREE
channel.description:
Well, this script used to be for sale for 900k a copy, but long story short, I = done with RS, so i am releasing for free. If you don't know about the script, read the topic I was selling it on here http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,25524.0.html For those who did buy, thank you so much, and to those who are going to leach it, your welcome :)
If you don't know, this is what the script is:
It will go through the Fight Caves in Tzharr, earning you Tokkul and experience. The experience is quite good, and you make some decent money with it to.
The script has many anti-ban elements to it, it has tons of randomness, there are some other scripts like this released, but none compare. They would eventually get stuck somewhere in the cave, and you would wake up, and bam, your banned. Not anymore, this script if it doesnt find a monster on the minimap it will randomally walk around the cave until it does.
On a level 81 in full rune a d long, it averages about 5 minutes a time through the cave, so your going about 12 times an hour, this means that the chance of you getting banned is very minimal because you don't have to move the mouse much, so it is not nearly as detectable as autofighters, because the mouse isnt moving like crazy trying to find a monster to fight, just make sure you have auto-retaliate on it, or your in trouble
The script is also auto-updating, the first time you run it, make sure you select always allow access to server bobert.blah blah blah and you'll never have to deal with that coming up again
Well, i guess thats it, the script is attached
[hr]
[b]edit by moparisthebest: Bobert5696 has been banned for scamming, but this script worked so I have removed the autoupdating part and reposted it for people to use and learn from.[/b]
